## Protocolo de Reviso T0 (batch_approve)

```python
# batch_approve l campos alternativos de lines  NUNCA apenas lines_added
LINE_FIELDS = ["lines_added", "lines_of_code", "total_lines_of_code", "lines_count", "handoff_lines"]
# threshold: >= 50L  APPROVED, < 10L  REJECTED, entre 10-49L  MANUAL (T0 review)
```

**Workflow:**
1. Worker gera handoff com `status: PENDING_REVIEW`
2. T0 roda `batch_approve.py`
3. Aprovados  fila `status: DONE`
4. Rejeitados  fila `status: AVAILABLE` (ticket volta)

